<section id="command-first">
<title>FIRST</title>
<indexterm><primary>FIRST</primary></indexterm>

<variablelist>

<varlistentry><term>Synopsis</term>
<listitem>
<synopsis><command>FIRST</command> <parameter>thing</parameter></synopsis>
</listitem>
</varlistentry>

<varlistentry><term>Description</term>
<listitem>
    <para>If <parameter>thing</parameter> is a word, outputs the first character of the word.
If <parameter>thing</parameter> is a list, outputs the first member of the list.
If <parameter>thing</parameter> is an array, outputs the origin of the array (that is, the index of the first element of the array).
</para>
</listitem>
</varlistentry>

<varlistentry><term>Example</term>
<listitem>
    <programlisting><userinput>SHOW FIRST [1 2 3]
</userinput>1</programlisting>

    <programlisting><userinput>SHOW FIRST "Hello
</userinput>H</programlisting>
</listitem>
</varlistentry>

</variablelist>

</section>

